name: Soligor 400mm F6.3
description:
Front and side view of the Soligor 400mm F6.3 T-mount lens (with M42 adapter)
Likely (based on serial number) manufactured by Kino/Kobori in Japan, late 1960s

A companion image to my video series exploring odd/cult/vintage lenses.
